-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
                   Icelandic Academic Vocabulary List (LÍNO-2) (v.1.0)
                        http://hdl.handle.net/20.500.12537/307
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Authors: Sigríður Ólafsdóttir and Auður Pálsdóttir

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Description
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

The Icelandic Academic Word List (Listi yfir íslenskan námsorðaforða, LÍNO-2) 
contains words from the Icelandic language corpus MÍNO. MÍNO can be downloaded 
from http://hdl.handle.net/20.500.12537/299.

Words in MÍNO that occur 100 times or more in the corpus are listed according 
to their frequency. The MÍNO frequency list can be downloaded from 
http://hdl.handle.net/20.500.12537/306.

The words in LÍNO-2 were chosen from the most frequent 5000 words found on the 
MÍNO frequency list. The selection of words goes beyond covering the most 
frequent words  in the Icelandic language and includes words that are used 
across various disciplines. These are Tier 2 words that play a key role when 
discussing a wide variety of complex issues, and that play an important role in 
education. LÍNO-2 contains 2,294 words (lemmas).

LÍNO-2 is intended as an important tool for teachers and authors of teaching 
materials and assessments, as well as for Icelandic learners seeking to 
strengthen their literacy skills in the Icelandic language.

The file LINO_frequeny_list_1_0.tsv contains four columns:
1. Lemma = the actual lemma
2. Orðfl. = a letter indicating the word class (in Icelandic: n=noun; s=verb; 
   l=adjective; a=adverb, c=conjunction)
3. Tíðnisæti = the actual frequency number on the MINO list. It refers to the
   rank of the word in the MINO frequency list mentioned above.
4. Fjöldi = the number of times the lemma appears in the MINO corpus.



-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
          Listi yfir íslenskan námsorðaforða í lagi 2 (LÍNO-2) (v.1.0)
                     http://hdl.handle.net/20.500.12537/307
